<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1908/513025.jpg" alt="Deadline for the 2019 Assegai Awards extended" width="250" height="221">The online entry for the Assegai Awards means that no matter where you find yourself, you will be able to submit your entries quickly and efficiently. There are 40 categories and entrants are welcome (and encouraged) to enter as many as they like. This is great news for those of you who have not yet submitted your entries - All you need to do is go to www.assegaiawards.co.za for all the help you need. We look forward to receiving your entries! Save the date: The Assegai Awards Ceremony will be held on Thursday, 7 November 2019, at The Polo Room/Inanda Club.